[
  {"email_id":"id123","from":"noreply@techservices.example","subject":"Reset your TechServices password","date":"2024-05-14T10:05:00Z","snippet":"To reset your TechServices password click the link below..."}
]

Now extract from <get_unread_emails_0/>.

